1.title: Radiate Happiness Mantra
1.plot: Welcome to the first day of the rest of your life! Today our mantra for the day is to RADIATE HAPPINESS! What does that mean? Can we take radiating happiness as literally as Betsy would like to? Sure, why not? Because there are not wrong answers, except when she says the wrong answer.

2.plot: Today's Daily Mantra - when you're out there fighting your fights, DON'T MAKE WAVES. MAKE FLATNESS. Trust us. This makes a LOT of sense and no - this is not a boob thing.

3.plot: Today your mantra, which Betsy actually came up with while she was trying to get out of a gift bag, is to MAKE YOUR PRESENCE YOUR PRESENTS! Deep.

220.title: Happy Birthday, Infinity!

232.plot: Self Diagnosis mode in full effect.

246.title: Finding Your Comfortable Spot
246.plot: Providing your own personal bliss can come in many forms.

247.plot: Sometimes the universe leaves you unexpected and confusing gifts.

248.plot: Growth can often be a one step forward, fifteen steps back scenario.

249.plot: Today, we practice nurturing and some of us get it wrong.

250.title: Orchid Love Continued

251.plot: How do you find inner peace? And is it legal?

252.title: We're Back
252.plot: So much has happened. Infinity Schwartz (the wannabe life coach) and Betsy (her probably high neighbor) are ready to share their 'knowledge'.

905.plot: Today is about not being the person you don't like.

imdb.title: Infinity and Betsy
plot: Soon to be life-coach Infinity Schwartz is determined to save her neighbor Betsy. This web series tracks their daily progress in the world of 'self-help'.
